reviewText: I could hardly catch English in this movie. I should have bought A Serbian Film than this.
FOR ME IT WAS UNWATCHABLE DID NOT MAKE IT THRU THE FIRST 10 MINUTES

Human Zoo is a great film! Except this Latin distribution DVD has NO English subtitles. It's only distributed with English subtitles in PAL format for France and Australia.  Amazon Instant Video should upload it for English speaking audiences.
